Usage: setSdpObjectStatus [-help]
                          -status <unplaced|placed|fixed|cover|softfixed> -name {name(s)} | -all

-help               # Prints out the command usage
-all                # (bool, optional)
-name {name(s)}     # sdp object name(s). (string, optional)
-status <unplaced|placed|fixed|cover|softfixed>
                    # sdp object placement status (string, required)